<div class="container">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>At Bluzen MHS, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We use Formspree, a secure third-party service, to collect form submissions. We may collect personal information including your name, contact details, job application data, and any other information you voluntarily provide through forms on our site.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Your information is used to respond to inquiries, process job applications, improve our services, and communicate relevant opportunities and updates.</p>

  <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
  <p>We do not sell or rent your personal data. We may share it with trusted partners only to deliver our staffing services, and only as necessary.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement standard security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.</p>

  <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
  <p>Our site may use cookies to enhance user experience. You can adjust your browser settings to decline cookies if preferred.</p>

  <h2>6. Third-Party Services and Links</h2>
  <p>We use Formspree to process form submissions securely. Please review their privacy policy at <a href='https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy/' target='_blank'>formspree.io</a> for more information. Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices or content.</p>

  <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You may request access to or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting us at <strong>stargrazer11hd@gmail.com</strong>.</p>

  <h2>8. Policy Updates</h2>
  <p>We reserve the right to update this policy. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <strong>stargrazer11hd@gmail.com</strong>.</p>
